Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She's way too self-conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for disturbing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, welcome, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you're back. We've got a harmonics test\Ntonight, so don't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that, Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your promotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're most welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up? Did something happen\Nto Miss Misato?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you see her collar tab?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The number of lines increased to two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That means that she's been promoted\Nfrom captain to major.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I didn't notice that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I wonder when...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are ya serious? You guys are pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you two have any compassion?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's a tough job for someone so young\Nto foster two junior high kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the only ones who've got\Nany human compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Units 00 and 02 are both on the edge\Nof the contamination zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They've reached their limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01 can still tolerate\Na little more though, can't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Lower the graph depth another 0.3.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's almost reached the contamination zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's still getting these readings? Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,His harmonics and sync rate are\Nalso catching up with Asuka's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what you call a gift, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like he was born to pilot an Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he doesn't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt that'll make him happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, you three.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, you did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Your harmonics value increased by\Neight points since the last test.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's still fifty points lower than mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but it's eight points in ten days.\NThat's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Such words of praise for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going on ahead, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:53.70,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and that was a postcard from\N"Mr. Wah" of Tokyo-2.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:59.00,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But you know, don't get all sulky\Nbecause you got dumped by a girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:02.92,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I was a kid, this area\Nwas filled with barracks{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But to be honest, I'm not really all that thrilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:04.76,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we were just grateful\Nif we got to eat that day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting praised like earlier doesn't make me\Nall that happy either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:09.64,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We didn't have the leisure to do anything\Nabout the people we liked.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All it does is make Asuka angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:13.35,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our parents are safe and food isn't a problem,\Nso we have a lot to be thankful for in this era.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why she got mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:20.48,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We live in a great time in which\Nwe can really enjoy happiness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I do wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That bothers you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:23.02,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You got that, Mr. Wah?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because all you ever do is worry\Nabout what other people think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:31.49,Sloppy Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H10081A&\pos(462.4,639)}Congratulations\NOn Your Promotion\NCelebration Spot\NReserved Today
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Suzuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah. He's the one who came up with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I, Kensuke Aida was the planner!\NKensuke Aida!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Aida.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, all I did was what\Nanybody would have done!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But why's the class rep here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I invited her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:06:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I invited her,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but that girl's unsociable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, Mr. Kaji's so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Mr. Kaji really that cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so much better than these dorks\Nthat it's like night and day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an insult to compare him to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd ya say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hear that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it still difficult for you to be\Nin this kind of situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just not used to being with
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do they have to be so noisy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A promotion...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That means that people have\Nacknowledged your work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they're happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't make you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's not like I'm not happy. I am, a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not the reason I work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did you join Nerv?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's been so long that I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's got to be Mr. Kaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I came directly from HQ. We just\Nhappened to meet on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's rather suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As if.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'd like to offer my congratulations,\NMajor Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I can't gripe to you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say, you jerk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway, it's unprecedented
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,for both the Commander and Vice Commander\Nto leave Japan together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That just shows how they trust you\Nto hold down the fort while they're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Ikari is at the South Pole right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The South Pole, a world of death\Nwhich permits no life to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Or should I simply call it Hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, we, mankind, are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're living things, and we're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because we're under the\Nprotection of science.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Science is the power of man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That arrogance is what caused the tragedy\Nof fifteen years ago, the Second Impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And here is the end result.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a greater punishment than we deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is truly the Dead Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet this is a world that has been purified,\Npurged of the original sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer a world where people live,\Nno matter how stained with sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Reporting. Telegram received\Nfrom Nerv Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,An Angel has been detected in orbit\Nabove the Indian Ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It appeared suddenly, two minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Search Satellite 6 moving to that orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Two minutes to contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We have video of the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's just ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Closing on target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Start search.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Data transmission commencing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Reception confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Commencing analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that an AT Field?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a new way of using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What incredible destructive power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an AT Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's using kinetic energy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like this Angel is a bomb in and of itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, the first blast was way off\Nand hit the Pacific.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And two hours later,\Nthe second shot struck there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, it has been steadily\Nadjusting for error.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That means it's learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:32.73,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(1329.045,861.05)\blur3}{\fs45\c&HDBFFDA&\3c&HC0D0C1&}Photo:\NSearch Satellite 7\N{\fs35}Maximum Magnification
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,N2 aerial mines had no effect on it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Angel's movements\Nsince then are unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and next time it'll drop itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that will give us a third Ashinoko Lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All five Fuji Lakes will be fused into\Na single body linked to the Pacific,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,taking Headquarters with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Commander Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We're unable to contact him\Ndue to the Angel's powerful jamming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the Magi's judgment?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They unanimously agree\Nin recommending evacuation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who's in charge now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Notify all of the Japanese government ministries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Under special declaration D-17,\Nprovided for under Nerv's authority,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,all residents within radius of 50km\Nare to evacuate immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask Matsushiro to back up the Magi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're abandoning this location?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but it's not necessary\Nto place everyone at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A D-17 Special Declaration has been\Nmade by the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:28.33,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(962.045,211.5)\c&H4A00F0&\3c&H41247C&}All Lanes Outgoing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All residents must evacuate to their\Ndesignated locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Beginning with the 6th and 7th blocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,move according to your district chief's\Ndirection immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The evacuation of the city is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In accordance with Department Alert C,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the evacuation of noncombatants and\ND class personnel has been completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to do this? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to throw away all three Evas\Nwith your selfish decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The chance of success is only 0.00001%!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not even one in ten thousand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not zero. I'm just banking on the Evas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Major Katsuragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I am currently in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do whatever I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroying Angels is my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your duty? Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for your own sake, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your revenge against the Angels!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAAAAAAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch it in our hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. We'll position the Evas\Nin the estimated drop zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll catch it while maintaining your\NAT Fields at full strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What if the Angel is far off course?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be out of luck, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What if the Evas aren't able\Nto withstand the impact?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're out of luck then too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Our chance of success?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,God only knows, is all I can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If we succeed, it'll truly be a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The only miracles with any value\Nare the ones you work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning, make it work somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but we have no other options\Nfor this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you call this an operation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, we really can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you don't want to, you can refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Regulations say you're technically supposed\Nto write a will. What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine, I don't plan on needing one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine too. I have no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Once this is over, I'll treat everyone\Nto a steak dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So I suppose steak defines a great dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she think a kid these days\Nwould be impressed with steak?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:14:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I say the Second Impact generation\Nhas really cheap standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What was with that "Yay!"?\NPretending you're so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If it helps Miss Misato feel good about\Nbeing in command, what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, since she's going to treat us,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:15.45,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(1313.864,625.5)\frz7.108\c&H12006F&}Tokyo Gourmet
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where we should have her take us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming with us this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the Angel's radio disturbance,\Nthe target has been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't determine the exact location,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but based on the data up until we lost it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the estimated point of impact\Ncalculated by the Magi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The range is this wide?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The distance from one side\Nto the other is enormous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Given the size of the target's AT Field,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,it could totally annihilate HQ by hitting\Nanywhere in this zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Given that, we'll station the Evas\Nat each of these three points.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,On what grounds is this dispersal based?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:14:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Intuition?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, a woman's intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How slipshod!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see our miracle getting further\Nand further away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Misato has never won the lottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka, why do you pilot an Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To exhibit my talent to the world, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean to prove that you exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to ask her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've asked Ayanami before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My, how intimate the two of you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what about you, Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know? What are you, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,One hundred twenty minutes\Nto estimated time of impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You all evacuate too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take care of this myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is our job as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let the kids risk\Ntheir lives by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the Evas are badly damaged,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,their AT Fields will protect the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside an Eva is the safest place to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, yesterday you asked me\Nwhy I joined Nerv.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was a man who lived\Nfor his research,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,for his dreams, to the exclusion of all else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never forgive him for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I even hated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He never took care of me,\Nmy mother or the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,His friends always said he was\Nvery sensitive and delicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But the truth was that he was just a weak person
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,running away from reality,\Nthe reality called his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He was like a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I readily agreed with my mother\Nwhen she decided to divorce him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,because she was always crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed to have come as a shock to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but at the time, I laughed at him because I felt\Nhe'd brought it on himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But he sacrificed himself to\Nsave my life at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Back during the Second Impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I didn't know whether I hated him\Nor loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that was clear to me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,was I wanted to destroy the Angels\Nwho caused the Second Impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So in order to do that, I joined Nerv.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, maybe I just want to\Nget revenge on my father,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so that I can free myself of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I mustn't run away. I mustn't run away.\NI mustn't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I must not run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Target has been sighted\Nat maximum magnification.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Distance is approximately 25,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All Evas, start positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have is a rough estimated trajectory\Nfrom optical sightings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Magi will guide you until\Nthe distance is 10,000 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, use your own judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving it all to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:20.87,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an1\pos(1181.282,874.6)}{\fs40\c&HB8EE56&\3c&H3D641F&}Maximum Magnification\N{\fs30}Relay: Optical observation Post 3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel approaching, approximate\Ndistance 20,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Commence operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Distance 12,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Field at maximum!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 02! Field to maximum!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Our wireless communications\Nhave been restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're receiving a message from\NCommander Ikari at the South Pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Connect him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My selfish decision has caused\NUnit 01 to incur damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The responsibility is entirely mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not a problem.\NDestroying Angels is the Evas' purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, we are fortunate to have sustained\Nsuch minimal damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, excellent work, Major Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, is the pilot of Unit 01 there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've received the report. Good work, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Major Katsuragi, I'll leave\Nthe rest in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:50.10,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\blur4\pos(998.864,193.5)\c&HC9FFA6&\3c&H3F6229&}All Lanes Incoming
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:55.81,Signs,,0,0,0,,New Tokyo-3 Loop 7
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Next station is New Miyanoshita,\NNew Miyanoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The exit will switch to the left side\Nat the next station.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're going to have to keep your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I withdrew a fortune, so I can even handle\Na full-course dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it's before payday...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:13.45,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ramen
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We know the state of your wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And Miss Perfect said she'd join us\Nif it was for ramen noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have a garlic ramen with no roast pork.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have shark fin with roast pork. Large!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go, one shark fin with roast pork!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Miss Misato?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.72,0:21:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard my father's words earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I finally understood what it's like\Nto feel happy when you're praised.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also realized
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that maybe I pilot the Eva because I wanted\Nto hear those words from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're piloting for something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:22:00.63,TBC Card,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1545.2,740.8)}TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.07,0:23:06.90,Preview Card,,0,0,0,,PREVIEW
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,An incident occurs during\Na simulation plug experiment,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.61,0:23:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the underground faciities are corrupted\None after another,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and finally Nerv is confronted with making\Nthe decision to self-destruct.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: "Angel Invasion"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And expect more fan service next time too!
